\b0 \cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\slmult1
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 Homeric virtue was (a) social (indexed to roles) and also (b) nonmoral at least in our modern dilapidated sense of \'91moral,\'92 referring more to qualities of strength, cunning, prowess, etc. \
\pard\tx360\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-360\sl360\slmult1
